---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Blue Team Operations | Paul Technologies">
  <Header />

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Blue Team Operations</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">
      Detection is useless without context. Alerts without analysis lead to
      fatigue, missed threats, and delayed response.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Capabilities</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 mb-8">
      <li>Log collection & normalization</li>
      <li>Detection engineering</li>
      <li>Threat hunting</li>
      <li>Alert triage & investigation</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Approach</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">
      We align detections to MITRE ATT&CK and focus on high-signal behaviors
      rather than noisy indicators.
    </p>

    <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-black px-6 py-3 rounded-md">
      Improve Detection
    </a>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
